The Glenn Beck Radio Show JAN-10-2014 FRI............PODCAST




The Glenn Beck Program



The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
The Glenn Beck Program - 1/10/14Friday, January 10, 2014 11:12 AM


Glenn will no longer sit by and support anyone who is the better of two evils.
  A perfect example is Chris Christie,
     and Glenn compares his stance on major views
        with those of the president...
            obviously there are some major similarities.

  Also, the playoffs are in full swing as the Superbowl inches close,
     so today's More On Trivia is between Indianapolis and New England. 

 Plus, Dana Loesch joins the show to discuss her new show starting on the Blaze.
